urls.title: Delta flight attendant tells wheelchair passenger that TSA will make him get off plane 'with their guns'
urls.description: Cory Lee of Georgia shared an incident that occurred on Nov. 13 when a Delta flight crew asked him to exit the aircraft before his wheelchair was brought to the door of the plane.

data.text: I have to agree with Lee, communication, education, awareness, and inclusion are key.  I need extra leg room for clotting issues #stroke. I was given a regular seat and told by @Delta wasn't their problem. https://t.co/EAh7f6fCbh
